
==== Resolved Summary: <%= @date %> for <%= @email %> ====

This is an automated email informing you that <%= %>
there <%= @issList.length == 1 ? "is 1 issue" : "are " + @issList.length.to_s + " issues" %>
 in Redmine that <%= @issList.length == 1 ? "is" : "are" %> assigned to or <%= %>
